catalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-19T00:10:09Z to 2025-06-19T00:26:09Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 00:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-19 00:26:09+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "io_util", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_processes", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n\n经过对提供的日志数据进行分析，提取到了以下关键信息：\n\n#### Detected Log Keys\n- `transport`\n- `Error while dialing`\n- `connection refused`\n\n#### Hypotheses\n\n根据日志分析，多个 `frontend` 服务实例（如 `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`）在调用下游服务时均遇到了 `connection refused` 的错误。\n\n- **Component**: `unknown (possible payment service)`\n- **Reason**: `connection refused` 可能指示端口配置错误或目标服务未启动\n- **Evidence**: \n  - 日志显示：`transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused`\n\n该错误模式表明可能存在下游服务的端口配置错误或者该服务未正确启动及监听。根据日志特征，怀疑故障与网络或服务配置相关。\n\n### JSON 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"connection refused\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"unknown (possible payment service)\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection refused error indicates potential port misconfiguration or service not running.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此结果建议检查系统中服务的端口配置和运行状态，尤其是被 `frontend` 服务调用的目标服务（如 payment service）的状态和网络配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "在故障期间的监控指标中，我注意到以下几个显著的异常调用链：\n\n### 异常指标检测\n1. **Node 内存异常**\n   - `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 在 `aiops-k8s-03` 呈现显著下降。\n   - 检测到正常中位值为 5081673728.0 变为故障中位值 4168708096.0，变化率达到 19.74%。\n\n2. **Pod 生命周期异常**\n   - `pod_processes` 在 `redis-cart-0` 中从 P99 1.0 增加到 2.0，变化率达到 66.67%。\n\n3. **Service 错误率异常**\n   - `frontend` 服务在多个 Pod (`frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`) 上的 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 显著升高。\n\n4. **数据库 IO 指标**\n   - 在 `tidb-tikv` 检测到 `io_util` 指标变动，P99 由 0.05 降至 0.02，变化率为 -85.71%。\n\n### 归因分析\n\n#### Hypotheses\n- **Node `aiops-k8s-03` 内存资源异常**\n  - Component: `aiops-k8s-03`\n  - Reason: `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 显著下降，可能由于系统进程或硬件问题。\n  - Evidence: 错误期间内存可用字节显著减少。\n\n- **Pod `redis-cart-0` 生命周期异常**\n  - Component: `redis-cart-0`\n  - Reason: `pod_processes` 从 1.0 增加到 2.0，指示发生了重启或内存泄漏。\n  - Evidence: Mid-fault process count increase.\n\n### 原始异常指标\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_processes\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 显著下降，可能由于系统资源异常或硬件故障。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常中位值为 5081673728.0，故障中位值为 4168708096.0。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes 在故障期间从 1.0 增加到 2.0，暗示 Pod 可能重启或发生故障。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"P99 变化率达 66.67%。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n我将继续分析其他指标以确认或否认这些假设。", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过对调用链数据的初步扫描，我们发现了一些显著的异常调用链和错误状态码，这些信息可能与故障相关。以下是分析中的关键发现：\n\n### 异常调用链和延迟分析\n1. **Redis 访问延迟异常**\n   - **调用链**: `cartservice->redis`\n   - **异常数据**: `正常平均时长: 1771.42ms`，`异常时段平均时长: 11740.65ms`，`异常发生次数: 1`\n   - **原因**: 响应时间显著增加，延迟倍数大于 6.63，存在显著的延迟现象。\n\n2. **ProductCatalogService 延迟异常**\n   - **调用链**: `frontend->productcatalogservice`\n   - **异常数据**: 多条调用链出现类似异常，正常平均时长与异常时段平均时长差距显著。\n   - 例如：\n     - `frontend->productcatalogservice` 正常: `9209.96ms` 异常: `11507.52ms` 发生次数: 3\n     - 在多个前端到产品目录调用中观察到显著延迟。\n\n### 错误状态分析\n1. **Checkout Service 连接错误**\n   - **调用链**: `checkoutservice->paymentservice`\n   - **错误状态码**: `连接错误，连接被拒绝`\n   - **各组件报告的错误状态**:\n     - `failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable`\n     - 连接错误 `desc = transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused` 出现频次较高。\n\n### 初步结论\n- **Redis 访问延迟**可能导致了部分性能缓慢。\n- **ProductCatalogService**在多个前端调用中显示延迟。\n- **Checkout Service**连接错误是一个关键问题可能导致支付处理失败。\n\n### 建议\n需要进一步调查这些调用链的上游服务更详细的请求排查，特别是支付处理连接错误的原因，并确认是否有更广泛的网络问题。Redis 的访问迟缓表明可能是资源或配置问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均时长: 1771.42ms, 异常时段平均时长: 11740.65ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均时长: 9209.96ms, 异常时段平均时长: 11507.52ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请进一步研究系统配置和相关调用链的具体实现，以解决故障。"}
